text: Ross Wilson (29 December 1909 - 25 March 1997) was a Canadian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1997 deaths Category:Canadian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Canada Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Toronto
